				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Previously, Nintendulator didn't implement proper DMC cycle-stealing (it was hardcoded to 4 cycles and didn't care about alignment). It <em>tries</em> to do so now, though I'm pretty sure it isn't 100% correct (specifically for the case of DMC fetch happening one cycle after a $2004 write).</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Quietust, QMT Productions
<br />P.S. If you don't get this note, let me know and I'll write you another.</div>
