				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The only caveat is that this gives you less time for PPU updates since sprite DMA should ideally be done first thing, followed by all the PPU bus accessing code. On the other hand, <em>wow</em>, you don't need to reread and compare the controller bytes! That's really spiffy, especially if you need to read more than 8 bits from each port. Nice finding!</div>

